data.description: Beautiful 5 bedroom 3 bath home in Decatur.  Open eat-in kitchen with granite countertops. Guest/In-law Suite with full bath on the main level for easy access. The master bedroom has crown molding and a large master bathroom with separate shower and tub and dual vanities. Large Bonus Room. NO HOA. 15 minutes to Downtown Atlanta, Airport, World of Coke, and all major highways.
